Mission.Author: Histidine
Mission.Description: Kite, burn and race across Comet Catcher in this challenging arena!
Mission.Name: Super Extreme Kodachi Rally
Mission.ScoringMethod: Earn points by killing mexes and bosses, and for completing rounds. Try not to take too long or lose your units!

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
Spring.SetGameRulesParam("seeker_introInCampaign", 0) local isCampaign = Spring.GetModOptions().commandertypes ~= nil and 1 or 0 Spring.SetGameRulesParam("seeker_isCampaign", isCampaign)
if (Spring.GetGameRulesParam("seeker_isCampaign") ~= 1) or (introInCampaign) then GG.mission.ExecuteTriggerByName("Initialization for Intro", -2) GG.mission.RunEvents(-2) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
if WG.Music then WG.Music.SetWarThreshold(0) WG.Music.SetPeaceThreshold(-1) end
-- force start when testing from Mission Editor -- not needed if run from Chobby campaign (a widget will do this) if not Spring.GetModOptions().commandertypes then Spring.SendCommands("forcestart") end

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Intro2") for unitID in pairs(units) do Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIRE_STATE, {0}, 0) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, 36214, {0}, 0) -- disable tactical AI end

TriggerLogic.Name: Console Message
TriggerLogic.Message: wololo

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
GG.SpawnPowerups(12, nil, true) GG.StartRound(-2) GG.RefreshObjDisplay()
local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("ObjMex") for unitID in pairs(units) do local health, maxHealth = Spring.GetUnitHealth(unitID) Spring.SetUnitMaxHealth(unitID, maxHealth/2) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Add Objective
TriggerLogic.Description: 7 Kodachis Defeat the Goliath Enemies: Glaives, Bandits, Darts, Scorchers, Daggers, Puppies, Blitzes, Reavers, Outlaws, Fencers, Maces, Pyros, Moderators Powerup every 30 seconds
TriggerLogic.Title: Boss

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: BEHOLD! OPTIC BLAST!

TriggerLogic.CodeStr: if (Spring.GetGameRulesParam("seeker_isCampaign") ~= 1) or (Spring.GetGameRulesParam("seeker_introInCampaign") == 1) then GG.mission.ExecuteTriggerByName("Intro") else GG.mission.ExecuteTriggerByName("Game Start") end

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Welcome back folks to another episode of SUPER EXTREME KODACHI RALLY!
Burn mexes! Torch raiders! KILL ANYONE WHO GETS IN YOUR WAY!

TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Intro2") for unitID in pairs(units) do Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIRE_STATE, {2}, 0) end
-- hide economy panel if WG.EconomyPanel then WG.EconomyPanel.SetEconomyPanelVisibility(false) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Add Objective
TriggerLogic.Description: 1 Kodachi 3 mexes Enemies: Glaives Powerup every 45 seconds
TriggerLogic.Title: Round 1

TriggerLogic.Message: ROUND ONE! Get ready!

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: --GG.SetRound(1) if (Spring.GetGameRulesParam("seeker_isCampaign") ~= 1) then GG.mission.ExecuteTriggerByName("Intro GUI Message") end

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message:
Welcome to General Saktoth's Super Extreme Kodachi Rally (SEEKeR!)
Your objective in each round is to destroy all the mexes, while killing enemy raiders who give chase and outsmarting fixed defenses. Each level adds increasingly deadlier challenges, so stay on your toes!
To help you out, there are powerups scattered around the map. Touch them with a Kodachi to activate them. More powerups will spawn at regular intervals.
If all your Kodachis are dead, you lose the round. Don't worry, you get to try again!

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: -- cleanup mex corpses (they block line of fire) -- solars too local features = Spring.GetAllFeatures() for i=1,#features do local featureID = features[i] local featureDefID = Spring.GetFeatureDefID(featureID) local featureDef = FeatureDefs[featureDefID] if featureDef.name == "staticmex_dead" or featureDef.name == "energysolar_dead" then Spring.DestroyFeature(featureID) end end

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: -- reset defense ranges Spring.SendCommands("luaui togglewidget Defense Range Zero-K") Spring.SendCommands("luaui togglewidget Defense Range Zero-K")

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: GG.EndRound() local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Koda") for unitID in pairs(units) do GG.SetUnitInvulnerable(unitID, true) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: VICTORY! A NEW SEEKeR CHAMPION!!

TriggerLogic.CodeStr: if GG.MissionGameOver then GG.MissionGameOver(true) else GG.mission.ExecuteTriggerByName("Victory Fallback") end

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Oooooh! Looks like you'll have to try again!
And our contestant wins the first round! A good start!
